Started this with intent doing a cover for "Tu Mere Rubaroo Hai" song from Maqbool movie. The music is composed by Vishal Bhardwaj and lyrics  penned by Gulzar. This is my rendition of the song. It is starkly different from original except for  the chorus of the original composition  "Tu mere rubaroo hai ...meri aankhon ki ibadat hai " part of the song.
